THE GAME
--------

  'Xaround' is a Workbench game where you have to move an 'X'
shape from one position to another on a game board, so that it
goes around all square zones, which are surrounded by 4 links.

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Many game boards to play with...

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50 kilobytes, so
 it takes little time to download ...although, you can play another
 of my Workbench games while downloading this game ;)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

